    <Title><![CDATA[Creating dynamic functions]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>As only users with the role <code>TEMPLATE_DEVELOPER</code> can edit the dynamic function elements, the function should be created inside the module folder: <code>/system/modules/[module name]/functions/</code>. To hide the function element from "Add content" Dialog set following property:</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
    <Section>
      <Image>
